description:
Watch this recorded session from Unreal Fest Seattle 2024 that explores the intricacies of MetaHuman rigs, shedding light on their composition and evolution.   

We explore the components of the MetaHuman rig, including LODs, meshes, blendshapes, skeletal structure, and facial animations; demonstrate how to leverage DNA libraries to answer rig-related questions; and look at the relationship between MetaHuman DNA (the underlying data) and RigLogic.

To learn more about MetaHuman, check out our website: https://www.unrealengine.com/en-US/metahuman
